 and say to your clients =E2=80=9Chey guys, I manage your money now,=E2=80=
=9D they might say =E2=80=9Cno you don=E2=80=99t.=E2=80=9D Sculptor=E2=80=
=99s clients are clients of the firm, but they are also clients of Jimmy Le=
