ecoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: =
#000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Sculptor ann=
ounced</a> that the Weinstein group put in a new offer for $12.76 per share=
, raising its own offer by 51 cents. Sculptor=C2=A0still says no: =E2=80=9C=
Notwithstanding its proposed price of $12.76 per Class A Share, the Special=
 Committee cannot support a transaction that has significantly less certain=
ty of closing than the transaction with Rithm.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Reading between the lines of the announcement =
you can see that Weinstein didn=E2=80=99t just raise his price, he also ans=
wered some of Sculptor=E2=80=99s previous complaints about certainty. Sculp=
tor=E2=80=99s board originally objected to the Weinstein proposal because i=
t didn=E2=80=99t have committed financing for the full $650 million or so r=
equired to do the deal:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Weinstein and friends provided equity =
commitment letters for $288 million.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px=
;">They planned to sell off Sculptor=E2=80=99s collateralized loan obligati=
on business, roughly one-third of the firm, to another buyer (called =E2=80=
=9CBidder H=E2=80=9D in <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
click/32571530.259423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhL=
zE0MDMyNTYvMDAwMTE0MDM2MTIzMDQwNTk1L255MjAwMDk5Mzl4MV9wcmVtMTRhLmh0bSN0Qk0/=
607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBb7e45eb3" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"item=
scope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !im=
portant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bot=
tom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Sculptor=E2=80=99s proxy</a>). =
But they didn=E2=80=99t have a signed deal with Bidder H, and their deal wa=
s conditional on getting it done; Sculptor worried that they wouldn=E2=80=
=99t be able to.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Somehow their cal=
culation of how much money they=E2=80=99d need was too low by $217 million,=
 leaving a funding gap.</li>
</ul>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The new proposal seems to resolve those issues=
<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; t=
ext-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-co=
